{"tid":2425582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！美軍戰略偵察機逼近廣東外海 刷新最近紀錄","createTime":"2021-02-27T12:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T21:37:30.000Z","uid":255749,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"908b2cbf223605a1fcef130eb5311cdeb02dcd89","tid":2425582,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國空軍一架RC-135U戰略偵察機飛近廣東外海偵察。<br />\n<br />\n內地智庫「南海戰略態勢感知」指，該偵察機早上由日本沖繩起飛，經巴士海峽飛到廣東外海偵察。最近距離中國劃定的領海基線不到47海里，刷新美國軍用飛機對中國抵近偵察距離最近的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n「南海戰略態勢感知」又指，對於美軍抵近偵察，中方要求美國要「適當顧及」。因為離中國太近，美軍執意抵近偵察，中國軍隊視距離遠近，通常也會採取跟蹤、伴飛和驅離等措施。<br />\n<br />\nRC-135U為電子情報偵察機，在機頭、翼端裝有天線，主要是執行搜集戰略電子偵察資訊任務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425564&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm258GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=30493895\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425564&h=d7f42bd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425564</a>"},{"pid":"e35fd218e15aaeb2e6ae245e2ad7acaf43884167","tid":2425582,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:22:53.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"cb4304b29e162d99b347d07231927ffbd2d6f672","tid":2425582,"uid":255749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"67aba6b05e4d9e218bfb4e99ac2fd008a6af7a01","tid":2425582,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:08:09.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"b7bd9c8e538057d9a0158694180d189bd0c5b299","tid":2425582,"uid":263183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:14:08.000Z","msg":"有上開連登時事台都知係拜登打算送架美軍偵察機俾中國換幻幻"},{"pid":"051e33449f3044848fefb10ba2d0837d5844f17a","tid":2425582,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T21:25:02.000Z","msg":"支那睇新聞先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56b334a9eab447e810d42ec044687339cf9c4c5","tid":2425582,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T21:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近距離中國劃定的領海基線不到47海里，刷新美國軍用飛機對中國抵近偵察距離最近的紀錄。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://glanfordcurling.com/data/112/images/DSC_3423web.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglanfordcurling.com%2Fdata%2F112%2Fimages%2FDSC_3423web.jpg&h=5e932152&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}